frames.caption: Three small monkeys are sitting in a steaming hot spring surrounded by vibrant pink cherry blossoms. The scene is serene and picturesque, with the monkeys appearing relaxed and content in the warm water. The setting is enhanced by the delicate snow and rocks around the hot spring.
frames.description: The image depicts a tranquil scene where three monkeys enjoy a hot spring bath amidst a backdrop of cherry blossoms. The setting suggests a peaceful, natural environment, possibly resembling a Japanese garden.
